&lt;li&gt;Strategic Sourcing: Proactively attract exceptional scientific talent for Activate’s programs, integrating our impact goals and specific scientific focus areas into a cohesive evaluation strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain Integrity: Ensure the selection process remains independent and credible while collaborating with the Development team on sponsor cultivation and fellow matching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
